snippet.title: Johnny Depp Gets Support From Wife Amber Heard Receiving Award At Palm Springs Film Fest

Saturday, January 2, 2016 - Johnny Depp and wife Amber Heard work the crowd at the Palm Springs Film Festival, where Johnny was to receive the Modern Master Award. Heard is also there to support her film "The Danish Girl." X17online.com
